photo\" title=\"Ben's photo\">Ben's photo<\/a> \u2022 <a href=\"\/wiki\/Canteens\" title=\"Canteens\">Canteens<\/a> \u2022 <a href=\"\/wiki\/Dogen%27s_baseball\" title=\"Dogen's baseball\">Dogen's baseball<\/a> \u2022 <a href=\"\/wiki\/Dogen%27s_knife\" title=\"Dogen's knife\" class=\"mw-redirect\">Dogen's knife<\/a> \u2022 <a href=\"\/wiki\/Dogen%27s_poison\" title=\"Dogen's poison\">Dogen's poison<\/a> \u2022 <a href=\"\/wiki\/Tom%27s_fake_beard\" title=\"Tom's fake beard\">Tom's fake beard<\/a> \u2022 <a href=\"\/wiki\/Files\" title=\"Files\">Files<\/a> \u2022 <a href=\"\/wiki\/Fish_biscuit\" title=\"Fish biscuit\">Fish biscuit<\/a> \u2022 <a href=\"\/wiki\/Hydra_television\" title=\"Hydra television\">Hydra television<\/a> \u2022 <a href=\"\/wiki\/Implant\" title=\"Implant\">Implant<\/a> \u2022 <a href=\"\/wiki\/Jughead_(bomb)\" title=\"Jughead (bomb)\">Jughead<\/a> \u2022 <a href=\"\/wiki\/Juliet%27s_tape\" title=\"Juliet's tape\">Juliet's tape<\/a> \u2022 <a href=\"\/wiki\/Lists\" title=\"Lists\">Lists<\/a> \u2022 <a href=\"\/wiki\/Mikhail%27s_document\" title=\"Mikhail's document\">Mikhail's document<\/a> \u2022 <a href=\"\/wiki\/Mystery_Tales_No._40\" title=\"Mystery Tales No. 40\">Mystery Tales No. 40<\/a> \u2022 <a href=\"\/wiki\/Richard%27s_items\" title=\"Richard's items\" class=\"mw-redirect\">Richard's items<\/a> \u2022 <a href=\"\/wiki\/Tape_recorder\" title=\"Tape recorder\">Tape recorder<\/a> \u2022 <a href=\"\/wiki\/Toxic_gas\" title=\"Toxic gas\">Toxic gas<\/a> \u2022 <a href=\"\/wiki\/Walkies\" title=\"Walkies\">Walkies<\/a> \u2022 <a href=\"\/wiki\/X-ray\" title=\"X-ray\">X-ray<\/a><\/div><\/td><\/tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td><\/td><\/tr><tr><td class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\">Miscellaneous<\/td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left:2px solid #fdfdfd;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\"><a href=\"\/wiki\/Book_club\" title=\"Book club\">Book club<\/a> \u2022 <a href=\"\/wiki\/Good_and_bad_people\" title=\"Good and bad people\">Good and bad people<\/a> \u2022 <a href=\"\/wiki\/Magic_box\" title=\"Magic box\">Magic box<\/a> \u2022 <a href=\"\/wiki\/O-Missions\" title=\"O-Missions\">O-Missions<\/a><\/div><\/td><\/tr><\/table><\/td><\/tr><\/table>\n<p><br \/>\n<\/p>\n<div class=\"metadata topicon\" id=\"featured-star\" style=\"position:absolute; top:-16px; right:12px; z-index:1\"><a href=\"\/wiki\/Lostpedia:Featured_Article_Selection\" \tclass=\"image image-thumbnail link-internal\" \t title=\"This is a featured article. Click here for more information.\"  \t \t><img src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP\/\/\/yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" \t alt=\"Featured Article\"  \tclass=\"lzy lzyPlcHld \" \t \tdata-image-key=\"LinkFA-star.png\" \tdata-image-name=\"LinkFA-star.png\" \t data-src=\"http:\/\/img2.wikia.nocookie.net\/__cb20061123002747\/lostpedia\/images\/thumb\/6\/60\/LinkFA-star.png\/16px-LinkFA-star.png\"  \t width=\"16\"  \t height=\"16\"  \t \t \t onload=\"if(typeof ImgLzy===&#39;object&#39;){ImgLzy.load(this)}\"  \t><noscript><img src=\"http:\/\/img2.wikia.nocookie.net\/__cb20061123002747\/lostpedia\/images\/thumb\/6\/60\/LinkFA-star.png\/16px-LinkFA-star.png\" \t alt=\"Featured Article\"  \tclass=\"\" \t \tdata-image-key=\"LinkFA-star.png\" \tdata-image-name=\"LinkFA-star.png\" \t \t width=\"16\"  \t height=\"16\"  \t \t \t \t><\/noscript><\/a><\/div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nPreprocessor node count: 12168\/300000\nPost\u2010expand include size: 143706\/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 31702\/2097152 bytes\nExpensive parser function count: 246\/400\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key lostpedia:pcache:idhash:22001-0!*!0!!en!2!* -->\n"},"langlinks":[{"lang":"ar","url":"http:\/\/ar.lostpedia.wikia.com\/wiki\/%D8%B1%D9%8A%D8%AA%D8%B4%D8%A7%D8%B1%D8%AF_%D8%A3%D9%84%D8%A8%D8%B1%D8%AA","*":"\u0631\u064a\u062a\u0634\u0627\u0631\u062f \u0623\u0644\u0628\u0631\u062a"},{"lang":"de","url":"http:\/\/de.lost